annotation.text: Using ApplicationId we will fetch Forms and their current max form version, based on sequence number
Temporary Form & FormVersion Ids are given to already saved forms.
In case any form is deleted, then we will set IsDeleted value for that form to true and sequence number to 0. And will update those forms in DB

If there are some changes made to form version like change in name or description, adding or removing a component, then we will increment its version number and set its Ids to 0(to insert new record for new form version)
